'''Qua'Tahc''' was the capital city of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Af'El/Legends|Af'El]] homeworld of the [[Defel/Legends|Defels]]. The city contained some of the most lucrative [[Meleenium/Legends|meleenium]] mines on the entire planet.

